hreaten%20witnesses%20and%20tamper%20evidence%20as%20he%20was%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bposition%20of%20command%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20presence%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime%20(SOC)%20raises%20a%20strong%20possibility%20of%20tampering%20with%20crucial%20evidence%2C%20including%20electronic%20evidence.%20The%20accused%20is%20an%20influential%20person%20and%20having%20worked%20more%20than%20nine%20years%20in%20an%20authoritative%20position%20can%20influence%2C%20and%20pressure%20the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20CM%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20was%20arrested%20yesterday%20for%20allegedly%20assaulting%20AAP%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%20at%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20on%20Monday.%20Ms%20Maliwal%20had%20alleged%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20kicked%20her%20in%20the%20chest%2C%20stomach%20and%20pelvic%20area%20and%20had%20brutally%20%26quot%3Bdragged%20her%20and%20pulled%20her%20shirt%20up%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20FIR%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20brutally%20assaulted%20by%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20when%20she%20went%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence.%20She%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20kicked%2C%20punched%20and%20abused%20by%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20who%20is%20the%20personal%20secretary%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%20The%2039-year-old%20also%20said%20that%20her%20clothes%20were%20torn%2C%20and%20she%20received%20severe%20injuries%20on%20her%20head%20and%20her%20leg%20during%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20new%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20Swati%20Maliwal%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20have%20any%20injuries%20and%20is%20even%20seen%20trying%20to%20free%20herself%20from%20the%20policewoman's%20grip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20Swati%20Maliwal%20have%20been%20trading%20bitter%20barbs%20as%20each%20pushed%20back%20against%20the%20other%20over%20the%20latter's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20video%20of%20May%2017