C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Felon-musk-to-launch-starlink-satellite-internet-service-in-bali-indonesia%2Famp_articleshow%2F110242629.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Dhoni%2C%20This%20Ex-India%20Star%20Was%20First-Choice%20Captain%20For%20CSK%20In%20IPL%202008%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greats%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20Whenever%20the%20name%20of%20Dhoni%20is%20taken%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20franchise%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20also%20comes%20along%20with%20it%20quite%20often%20than%20not.%20This%20is%20because%20Dhoni%20has%20played%20for%20the%20side%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20league%20in%202008.%20He%20has%20featured%20for%20CSK%20throughout%20IPL%2C%20barring%20the%20two%20seasons%20in%202016%20and%202017%20when%20the%20side%20was%20banned.%20During%20his%20long%20stint%20with%20the%20team%2C%20Dhoni%20also%20led%20the%20side%20to%20record-equalling%20five%20IPL%20titles.%20Be%20it%20from%20the%20CSK%20franchise%20or%20its%20fans%2C%20the%20player%20has%20earned%20immense%20love%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20former%20India%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virender%20Sehwag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F86-virender-sehwag-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirender%20Sehwag%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20an%20intriguing%20revelation.%20While%20speaking%20to%20Fever%20FM%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Dhoni%20was%20not%20the%20first-choice%20captain%20for%20the%20franchise.%20According%20to%20Sehwag%2C%20VB%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20who%20was%20man-in-charge%20to%20buy%20players%20for%20CSK%20ahead%20of%20the%20inaugural%20IPL%20season%2C%20had%20approached%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVB%20Chandrashekhar%20was%20selecting%20the%20players%20for%20CSK.%20He%20phone-called%20me%20and%20said%2C%20'We%20want%20you%20to%20play%20for%20CSK.%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20want%20you%20to%20be%20their%20icon.%20Don't%20accept%20the%20offer'.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20fine%2C%20we%20will%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sehwag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinally%2C%20I%20received%20the%20offer%20from%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20to%20be%20their%20icon%20player%20and%20I%20accepted%20it.%20I%20didn't%20go%20into%20the%20auction.%20If%20I%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20auction%2C%20CSK%20would've%20bought%20me%20and%20made%20me%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20side.%20But%20then%2C%20they%20bought%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20made%20him%20the%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20Sehwag%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESehwag%20joined%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20(now%20Delhi%20Capitals)%20and%20played%20six%20seasons%20for%20the%20side%20before%20moving%20to%20Kings%20XI%20Punjab%20(now%20Punjab%20Kings)%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%20He%20played%20two%20editions%20of%20the%20new%20side%20and%20then%20hanged%20up%20his%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716089160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4pjdlu8o_ms-dhoni-bcci_625x300_02_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-ms-dhoni-this-ex-india-star-was-first-choice-captain-for-csk-in-ipl-2008-5686363%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20led%20CSK%20to%20record-equalling%20five%20IPL%20titles.%20Be%20it%20from%20the%20CSK%20franchise%20or%20its%20fans%2C%20the%20player%20has%20earned%20immense%20love%20and%20respect.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-ms-dhoni-this-ex-india-star-was-first-choice-captain-for-csk-in-ipl-2008-5686363%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-ms-dhoni-this-ex-india-star-was-first-choice-captain-for-csk-in-ipl-2008-5686363%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-ms-dhoni-this-ex-india-star-was-first-choice-captain-for-csk-in-ipl-2008-5686363%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunak's%20Conservative%20party%20trails%20opposition%20by%2018%20points%3A%20Opinion%20poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716087635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110242920%2Cimgsize-59866.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunaks-conservative-party-trails-opposition-by-18-points-opinion-poll%2Farticleshow%2F110242853.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110242853.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBRITAIN-POLITICS-Britain's%20Conservatives%20trail%20Labour%20by%2018%20points%2C%20says%20Opinium%20poll%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunaks-conservative-party-trails-opposition-by-18-points-opinion-poll%2Farticleshow%2F110242853.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunaks-conservative-party-trails-opposition-by-18-points-opinion-poll%2Famp_articleshow%2F110242853.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Frishi-sunaks-conservative-party-trails-opposition-by-18-points-opinion-poll%2Famp_articleshow%2F110242853.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20Kohli%2C%20Du%20Plessis%20Dedicates%20Player%20Of%20The%20Match%20Award%20vs%20CSK%20To...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20skipper%20Faf%20du%20Plessis%20on%20Saturday%20dedicated%20his%20player-of-the-match%20award%20to%20pacer%20Yash%20Dayal%2C%20who%20kept%20his%20cool%20in%20the%20final%20over%20to%20seal%20a%2027-run%20win%20over%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20in%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20final%20IPL%20play-off%20spot.%20Du%20Plessis%20was%20adjudged%20the%20player-of-the-match%20for%20his%2054%20off%2039%20balls%20which%20along%20with%20Virat%20Kohli's%2047%20set%20the%20foundation%20as%20RCB%20posted%20a%20solid%20218%20for%20five%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20CSK%20needed%20to%20score%20200%20plus%20to%20qualify%20and%20they%20came%20agonisingly%20close%20to%20sealing%20the%20berth%20with%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20going%20hammers%20and%20tongs%20towards%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20needed%2017%20off%20the%20final%20over%20but%20Dayal%20held%20his%20nerves%20despite%20being%20hit%20for%20a%20towering%20six%20by%20Dhoni%20in%20the%20first%20ball%20to%20seal%20it%20in%20the%20end%20for%20RCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20dedicate%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20Match%20(award)%20to%20Yash%20Dayal!%20I%20said%20to%20him%20pace%20off%20on%20this%20wicket%20is%20the%20best%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Du%20Plessis%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20night!%20Such%20a%20great%20atmosphere.%20Just%20a%20pleasure%20to%20finish%20the%20season%20in%20front%20of%20the%20home%20fans.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20rain%20falling%20on%20the%20pitch%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20that%20moisture.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20day-five%20Test%20match%20in%20Ranchi!%26quot%3B%20Rain%20threat%20was%20looming%20on%20the%20match%20and%20there%20was%20a%2040-minute%20rain%20interruption%20too%20but%20it%20didn't%20matter%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20contributions%20from%20many%20batters%20at%20good%20strikes%2C%20I'm%20really%20proud.%20We%20were%20defending%20175%20(and%20neither%20201%20nor%20218)!%20We%20tried%20to%20get%20the%20ball%20changed%20tonight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crazy%3B%20even%20when%20we%20weren't%20winning%2C%20we%20had%20the%20fans%20here.%20It%20was%20set%20up%20perfectly%20-%20CSK%20vs%20RCB!%20Incredible.%26quot%3B%20CSK%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20said%20missing%20out%20on%20key%20players%20made%20a%20huge%20difference%20as%20they%20finished%20fifth%20in%20the%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20was%20a%20good%20wicket%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20was%20spinning%20and%20gripping%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20but%20I%20think%20200%20on%20this%20ground%20was%20gettable.%20We%20kept%20losing%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20one%20or%20two%20hits%2C%20sometimes%20that%20can%20happen%20in%20a%20T20%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretty%20happy%20with%20what%20the%20target%20was%2C%20to%20sum%20up%20the%20season%2C%20I%20am%20pretty%20happy%20to%20have%20seven%20wins%20out%20of%2014%20games.%20Just%20couldn't%20get%20over%20the%20line%20in%20the%20last%20two%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20kind%20of%20injuries%20we%20had%2C%20missing%20out%20on%20two%20frontline%20bowlers%2C%20not%20having%20(Devon)%20Conway%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order%20as%20well%2C%20I%20think%20missing%20out%20on%20three%20key%20players%20made%20a%20huge%20difference.%26quot%3B%20Talking%20about%20the%20spate%20of%20injuries%20which%20affected%20the%20team%2C%20Gaikwad%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20many%20challenges%20for%20us%20right%20throughout%20the%20first%20game.%20Injury%20to%20Fizz%20(Mustafiur%20Rahman)%2C%20then%20injruy%20to%20(Matheesha)%20Pathirana%20as%20well%2C%20he%20came%20back%20and%20then%20again%20Pathirana%20missed%20out.%20When%20you%20have%20injuries%20around%2C%20you%20have%20to%20get%20that%20balance%20in%20the%20team%20and%20pick%20it%20(the%20team)%20for%20every%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20season%20sums%20up%20well%20where%20we%20had%20to%20tinker%20around%20with%20our%20playing%20XI%2C%20considering%20the%20injuries%20and%20all%20the%20illness%20(of%20the%20players)%20as%20well.%20Happy%20with%20the%20seven%20wins%2C%20couldn't%20get%20over%20the%20line%20though.%20Happy%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%2010%20from%20the%20last%202%20balls%20in%20our%20last%20knockout%20game%20last%20year%20so%20this%20was%20a%20similar%20situation%2C%20things%20didn't%20go%20our%20way%20(this%20season)%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20top%20run-scorer%20this%20season%20but%20he%20said%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20as%20he%20couldn't%20take%20the%20team%20to%20the%20play-offs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20personal%20milestones%20don't%20really%20matter%20a%20lot%2C%20after%20all%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20to%20win.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20getting%20there%20it's%20a%20disappointment.%20Doesn't%20matter%20if%20you%20score%20100%20runs%20or%20500-600%20runs%20in%20a%20season.%20I%20am%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716087540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fv0e4jo_du-plessis-bcci_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frcb-skipper-faf-du-plessis-big-gesture-dedicates-player-of-the-match-award-to-this-player-5694387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CSK%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20needed%2017%20off%20the%20final%20over%20but%20Dayal%20held%20his%20nerves%20despite%20being%20hit%20for%20a%20towering%20six%20by%20Dhoni%20in%20the%20first%20ball%20to%20seal%20it%20in%20the%20end%20for%20RCB.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Frcb-skipper-faf-du-plessis-big-gesture-dedicates-player-of-the-match-award-to-this-player-5694387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.amp