ent%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parents%20Of%20Israeli%20Woman%20Found%20Dead%20In%20Gaza%20Thankful%20To%20Have%20A%20Grave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGerman-Israeli%20Shani%20Louk's%20father%20says%20that%20finally%20laying%20his%20daughter%20to%20rest%20will%20be%20a%20gift%20after%20her%20body%20was%20recovered%20from%20Gaza%2C%20months%20after%20she%20was%20killed%20in%20Hamas'%20Oct.%207%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELouk%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20tattoo%20artist%2C%20was%20celebrating%20with%20friends%20at%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%20just%20inside%20Israel%20before%20it%20was%20attacked%20by%20gunmen%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group.%20Her%20body%20was%20soon%20seen%20in%20a%20video%2C%20slung%20across%20the%20back%20of%20a%20pickup%20truck%2C%20surrounded%20by%20gunmen%20and%20paraded%20through%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20informed%20her%20parents%2C%20Nissim%20and%20Ricarda%20Louk%2C%20that%20their%20daughter's%20body%20had%20been%20found%20by%20Israeli%20commandos%20in%20Gaza.%20Nissim%20Louk%20said%20that%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20he%20had%20viewed%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20saw%20the%20tattoos%20on%20her%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BNow%20she%20will%20have%20her%20own%20place%20next%20to%20us%20and%20we%20can%20go%20there%20whenever%20we%20want.%20And%20she%20can%20rest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20funeral%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Sunday%2C%20which%20is%20Ricarda%20Louk's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Shani%20said%20'let's%20give%20my%20mother%20a%20birthday%20present%20and%20let's%20go%20back%20and%20be%20close%20to%20her'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20Shani's%20grave%20nearby%20would%20be%20a%20comfort%2C%20said%20Ricarda%20Louk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B