ns-against-csk-in-ipl-2024%2Farticleshow%2F110242556.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110242556.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnushka%20Sharma%20cheered%20for%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20at%20the%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20on%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20celebrating%20their%20victory%20against%20CSK.%20In%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20actress%20had%20announced%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20son%20Akaay%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20London.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anger%2C%20Anxiety%2C%20Acrimony%3A%20Slovaks%20Weigh%20What%20Led%20To%20PM%20Fico%20Shooting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESlovak%20opposition%20party%20leader%20Michal%20Simecka%2C%20who%20described%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Robert%20Fico%20this%20week%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20democracy%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20he%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20child%20had%20received%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20experience%20is%20not%20uncommon%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20extreme%20political%20and%20personal%20animosities%20in%20Slovakia%20and%20across%20Europe%20that%20formed%20the%20backdrop%20to%20the%20shooting%20of%20Fico%2C%20who%20was%20still%20in%20intensive%20care%2C%20two%20days%20after%20being%20shot%20at%20close%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlovaks%20like%20Lubos%20Oswald%2C%20a%2041-year-old%20councillor%20in%20Handlova%2C%20Slovakia%2C%20where%20the%20shooting%20took%20place%2C%20felt%20a%20tragedy%20may%20have%20been%20in%20the%20making%20following%20years%20of%20deepening%20splits%20within%20the%20population%20and%20toxic%20political%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20go%20on%20like%20this%20anymore%3A%20two%20neighbours%20hating%20each%20other%20for%20not%20having%20the%20same%20political%20opinions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Reuters%20outside%20the%20shopping%20mall%20in%20the%20town%20where%20the%20assailant%2C%20a%20former%20security%20guard%2C%20fired%20five%20shots%20at%20Fico%20as%20he%20greeted%20supporters%20after%20an%20off-site%20cabinet%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20I%20feel%20in%20the%20local%20council.%20People%20try%20to%20stir%20up%20emotions%20and%20hatred%2C%26quot%3B%20Oswald%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20following%20the%20shooting%2C%20politicians%20across%20the%20spectrum%20have%20sought%20to%20ease%20anxiety%2C%20with%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Robert%20Kalinak%20calling%20for%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bto%20embark%20on%20a%20path%20of%20tolerance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20echoes%20of%20previous%20debates%2C%20Kalinak%2C%20a%2053-year-old%20lawyer%20seen%20in%20Slovakia%20as%20Fico's%20right-hand%20man%2C%20accused%20opposition%20parties%20and%20the%20media%20of%20fanning%20acrimony%20by%20encouraging%20protests%20against%20government%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrustration%20from%20endless%20losses...%20has%20led%20us%20to%20where%20we%20are%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalinak%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20suspect%20became%20radicalised%20because%20voters%20gave%20power%20to%20a%20Fico%20ally%2C%20Peter%20Pellegrini%2C%20in%20April's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20marched%20throughout%20the%20country%20of%205.4%20million%20since%20Fico%20returned%20to%20government%20last%20October%2C%20calling%20his%20policies%20a%20power%20grab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20putting%20his%20stamp%20on%20the%20whole%20political%20scene.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20he%20would%20done%20it%20more%20carefully%2C%20now%20he%20has%20a%20perfect%20blueprint%20given%20by%20(Hungarian%20leader)%20Victor%20Orban%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bratislava%20International%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20President%20Samuel%20Abraham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFICO%20PREDICTED%20A%20POLITICAL%20MURDER%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFico%20embarked%20on%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20changes%20which%20have%20raised%20concern%20over%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20including%20scrapping%20a%20prosecution%20branch%20dealing%20with%20high%20crime%20as%20well%20as%20plans%20to%20ease%20punishments%20for%20graft%2C%20revamp%20public%20media%20and%20limit%20the%20influence%20of%20non-governmental%20organisations.%20He%20has%20also%20ended%20government%20military%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterior%20Minister%20Matus%20Sutaj%20Estok%20said%20the%20suspect%20listed%20government%20policies%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20dismantling%20the%20special%20prosecutor's%20office%20that%20deals%20with%20high-level%20corruption%2C%20and%20its%20plans%20to%20reform%20the%20public%20broadcaster%20as%20reasons%20for%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFico%20had%20long%20accused%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20independent%20journalists%20of%20doing%20the%20opposition's%20bidding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20he%20warned%20that%20language%20by%20opposition%20supporters%20was%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20vulgar%20and%20swear%20at%20government%20politicians%20on%20the%20street%20...%20I%20am%20only%20waiting%20until%20this%20frustration%20...%20morphs%20into%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20leading%20government%20politician.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20not%20named%20the%20suspect%2C%20but%20Reuters%20has%20matched%20photographs%20of%20him%20with%20a%20man%20pictured%20in%20a%20protest%20against%20Fico%20in%20April%2C%20holding%20a%20banner%20reading%20%26quot%3BPEACE%20PROSPERITY%20(West)%2FWAR%20POVERTY%20(East)%26quot%3B%20and%20chanting%20%26quot%3Bshame%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20slogans%2C%20some%20of%20them%20vulgar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20Slovaks%2C%20anxiety%20had%20increased%20since%20parliamentary%20election%20campaign%20last%20year%2C%20during%20which%20President%20Zuzana%20Caputova%20accused%20Fico%2C%20who%20had%20called%20her%20a%20U.S.%20puppet%2C%20of%20inciting%20hatred%20against%20her%2C%20saying%20she%20had%20received%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenka%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20social%20worker%20from%20Bratislava%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bsociety%20has%20two%20poles%20...%20There%20are%20people%20who%20love%20(Fico)%20and%20there%20are%20others%20who%20hate%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20in%20the%20same%20underground%20passage%20in%20central%20Bratislava%20to%20take%20refuge%20from%20heavy%20rain%20above%2C%20Veronika%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20architect%2C%20said%20the%20upcoming%20European%20elections%20in%20June%20added%20to%20widespread%20unease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20tense%20...%20It's%20more%20and%20more%20aggressive%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20only%20in%20Slovakia%2C%20but%20worldwide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716085980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fj0mg9rmo_robert-fico-shot_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fanger-anxiety-acrimony-slovaks-weigh-what-led-to-pm-fico-shooting-5686499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Slovak%20opposition%20party%20leader%20Michal%20Simecka%2C%20who%20described%20an%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Robert%20Fico%20this%20week%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20democracy%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20he%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20child%20had%20received%20death%20threats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fanger-anxiety-acrimony-slovaks-weigh-what-led-to-pm-fico-shooting-5686499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fanger-anxiety-acrimony-slovaks-weigh-what-led-to-pm