0as%20well.%20When%20you%20have%20injuries%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20balance%20the%20squad.%20I%20couldn't%20get%20over%20the%20line%2C%20but%20these%20things%20can%20happen.%20For%20me%2C%20personal%20milestones%20don't%20matter%20a%20lot.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20ultimate%20prize%20is%20to%20win.%20We%20couldn't%20get%20it%2C%20so%20personally%2C%20I'm%20slightly%20disappointed%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaikwad%20was%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20CSK%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%20RCB%20put%20on%20a%20fine%20score%20of%20218%2F5%20on%20the%20board%2C%20with%20skipper%20Faf%20Du%20Plessis%20(54%20in%2039%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20(47%20in%2029%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20putting%20on%20a%2078-run%20partnership%2C%20setting%20a%20fine%20platform%20for%20Rajat%20Patidar%20(41%20in%2023%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Cameron%20Green%20(38*%20in%2017%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20to%20put%20on%20a%2071-run%20stand%20for%20the%20third%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECameos%20from%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20(14%20in%20six%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20six)%20and%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20(16%20in%20five%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20took%20RCB%20to%20a%20200-run%20plus%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20needed%20to%20restrict%20CSK%20below%20201%20runs%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20playoffs%20and%20surpass%20their%20net-run-rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20chase%20of%20219%20runs%20and%20the%20task%20of%20scoring%20201%20runs%20at%20least%20to%20book%20the%20top%20four%20spot%2C%20CSK%20lost%20two%20wickets%20early%20and%20were%20reduced%20to%2019%2F2.%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20(61%20in%2037%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20(33%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20put%20up%20a%2066-run%20stand%20to%20bring%20the%20side%20into%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20sunk%20CSK%20to%20129%2F6%2C%20but%20a%20partnership%20between%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20(42*%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20MS%20Dhoni%20(25*%20in%2013%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20threatened%20to%20take%20the%20match%20away%20from%20RCB.%20However%2C%20Yash%20Dayal%20defended%2011%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20over%2C%20restricting%20CSK%20to%20just%20191%2F7%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20is%20in%20fourth%20place%20with%20seven%20wins%20and%20seven%20losses%2C%20with%2014%20points.%20CSK%20is%20in%20the%20fifth%20spot%20with%20seven%20wins%20and%20seven%20losses%2C%20but%20they%20have%20slid%20down%20to%20fifth%20due%20to%20a%20lower%20net-run%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716084000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2pcc8mg_ruturaj-gaikwad-bcci_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-pinpoints-only-factor-that-resulted-in-csks-elimination-from-ipl-2024-5694454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaikwad%20displayed%20a%20sloppy%20performance%20against%20RCB%20on%20Saturday.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20for%20a%20golden%20duck%20on%20the%20first%20ball%20of%20the%20second%20inning%20by%20Glenn%20Maxwell.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-pinpoints-only-factor-that-resulted-in-csks-elimination-from-ipl-2024-5694454%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-pinpoints-only-factor-that-resulted-in-csks-elimination-from-ipl-2024-5694454%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-pinpoints-only-factor-that-resulted-in-csks-elimination-from-ipl-2024-56