%20can%20filter%20Google%20Trends%20results%20for%20specific%20locations%20and%20timeframes.%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Mark%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20this%20example%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20see%20how%20often%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20was%20searched%20on%20Google%20News%20over%20the%20last%2030%20days%20in%20the%20United%20States%20in%20all%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20Google%20Trends%20search%20for%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20shows%20a%20graph%20measuring%20%26quot%3Binterest%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20red%20arrow%20illustrating%20peak%20interest%20in%20the%20company.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664642ec14fb5b23cc5d4913%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221544%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20customized%20chart%20will%20change%20every%20time%20a%20different%20variant%20is%20chosen.%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Mark%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20see%20above%20is%20a%20peak%20on%20April%2026%2C%202024%2C%20just%20one%20day%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-earnings-alphabet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet's%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20call%2C%20during%20which%20it%20reported%20major%20beats%20and%20the%20company's%20first%20dividend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20the%20%26quot%3BInterest%20over%20time%26quot%3B%20graph%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BInterest%20by%20subregion%26quot%3B%20graph%20%E2%80%94%20where%20you%20can%20specify%20where%20in%20the%20country%20(metro%2C%20city%2C%20or%20subregion)%20the%20search%20was%20the%20most%20popular.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20shows%20a%20Google%20Trends%20map%20labeled%20%26quot%3Binterest%20by%20subregion%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20red%20arrow%20pointing%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BMetro%2