%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4o%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20already%20available%20as%20a%20chatbot%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-chatgpt-at-work-job-save-time-ai-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20many%20workers%20use%20for%20boring%2C%20text-based%20tasks.%20Free%20ChatGPT%20users%20are%20stuck%20with%20GPT-3.5%20but%20get%20limited%20access%20to%20a%20handful%20of%20responses%20from%20GPT-4o%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fchatgpt%2Fpricing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20pricing%20page%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ChatGPT%20Plus%20membership%20costs%20%2420%20a%20month%20and%20includes%20more%20answers%20from%20the%20faster%20GPT-4o%20model%2C%20access%20to%20GPT-4%2C%20and%20features%20like%20an%20image%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20previously%20tried%20and%20grown%20frustrated%20with%20ChatGPT's%20inability%20to%20write%20non-robotic-sounding%20emails%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20GPT-4o%20would%20actually%20help%20me%20out%20for%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20ChatGPT's%20%26quot%3Btemporary%20chat%26quot%3B%20feature%20to%20prevent%20the%20chatbot%20from%20spitting%20out%20similar%20responses%20based%20on%20previous%20answers%2C%20I%20tested%20three%20available%20versions%20of%20the%20chatbot%20%E2%80%94%20GPT-3.5%2C%20GPT-4%2C%20and%20GPT-4o%20%E2%80%94%20using%20three%20different%20email%20prompts%20to%20see%20if%20GPT-4o%20is%20superior%20to%20the%20earlier%20versions.%20Here's%20what%20I%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInterview%20requests%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20text%20recreation%20of%20a%20conversation%20between%20the%20author%20and%20GPT%204o.%20The%20author%20is%20asking%20the%20chatbot%20to%20write%20an%20email%20about%20the%20history%20of%20generative%20AI.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664929d120abc1efe8fb62b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT's%20newest%20model%20gave%20the%20shortest%20answer%20for%20this%20prompt.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20emails%20I%20send%20at%20my%20job%2C%20so%20I%20was%20an%20expert%20on%20how%20they%20should%20be%20structured.%20I've%20tried%20having%20GPT%20write%20these%20emails%2C%20but%20it%20never%20works%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20emails%20ChatGPT%20constructs%20are%20always%20extremely%20long%20and%20ridiculously%20official-sounding.%20I'm%20sending%20an%20email%2C%20not%20a%20quill-and-inkpot%20letter%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fking-charles-iii-reign-so-far-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKing%20of%20England%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20hoped%20GPT-4o%20would%20change%20its%20ways%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20teach%20an%20old%20chatbot%20new%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20prompt%20I%20gave%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECan%20you%20write%20an%20email%20to%20an%20expert%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20interviewing%20about%20the%20history%20of%20generative%20AI%20models%3F%20I%20want%20the%20email%20to%20be%20brief%20and%20friendly.%20Let%20the%20expert%20know%20I%20work%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPT-4o%20returned%20the%20shortest%20draft%2C%20which%20I%20was%20grateful%20for.%20However%2C%20I%20did%20find%20it%20odd%20that%20the%20chatbot%20wrote%20that%20I%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhonored%26quot%3B%20to%20interview%20a%20subject.%20Do%20not%20worry%2C%20future%20interview%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20I%20will%20not%20come%20off%20this%20strong%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20older%20models%20provided%20lengthier%20answers.%20I%20did%20find%20it%20interesting%20that%20these%20models%20made%20up%20topics%20my%20fake%20source%20and%20I%20could%20discuss%2C%20and%20that%20they%20were%20topical.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20older%20GPT-4%20model%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20faux%20interview%20would%20%26quot%3Bfocus%20on%20the%20key%20milestones%20and%20future%20implications%20of%20generative%20AI%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPT-4o's%20answer%20wasn't%20quite%20as%20detailed%20%E2%80%94%20it%20took%20the%20%26quot%3Bbrief%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20my%20request%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20GPT-4o%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EScheduling%20a%20meeting%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20text%20recreation%20of%20a%20conversation%20between%20the%20author%20and%20GPT%204o.%20The%20author%20is%20asking%20the%20chatbot%20to%20write%20an%20email%20to%20set%20up%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20with%20a%20boss.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66492acf9fc063e829b2a6fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20three%20models%20gave%20satisfactory%20responses%20to%20this%20prompt.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESending%20meeting%20emails%20isn't%20particularly%20difficult%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20easier%20to%20have%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20or%20something%20%E2%80%94%20else%20write%20them%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20second%20prompt%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20want%20to%20schedule%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20with%20my%20boss%20to%20discuss%20an%20ongoing%20project.%20Can%20you%20write%20an%20email%20asking%20to%20put%20something%20on%20the%20calendar%20this%20month%3F%20I%20want%20the%20email%20to%20be%20brief%20and%20conversational.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20that%20all%20three%20models%20constructed%20their%20emails%20concisely%20and%20similarly.%20My%20simple%20and%20straightforward%20prompt%20may%20have%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20interesting%20that%20the%20previous%20generation%2C%20GPT-4.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Easked