try%20by%20far%26quot%3B%20and%20branded%20the%20Democrat%20as%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20bullshit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20fired%2C%20get%20out%20of%20here%20Joe!%26quot%3B%20he%20called%20out%20to%20laughter%20from%20the%20pro-gun%20crowd%2C%20telling%20them%20Biden%20was%20coming%20for%20their%20firearms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20is%20fending%20off%20multiple%20criminal%20indictments%20for%20his%20unprecedented%20attempt%20to%20overthrow%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%20and%20was%20twice%20impeached%20as%20president%2C%20told%20the%20crowd%20Biden%20is%20%26quot%3Bcrooked%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Biden%20were%20Republican%2C%20he%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20the%20electric%20chair%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20meanwhile%20was%20stumping%20in%20the%20key%20southern%20state%20of%20Georgia%2C%20which%20the%20Democrat%20narrowly%20won%20in%202020%2C%20as%20he%20sought%20support%20from%20African%20Americans%20--%20a%20crucial%20element%20in%20his%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20democracy%20is%20really%20on%20the%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20supporters%20at%20Mary%20Mac's%20Tea%20Room%2C%20a%20Black-owned%20restaurant%20in%20Atlanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20opponent's%20not%20a%20good%20loser.%20But%20he%20is%20a%20loser%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20to%20applause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20only%20obsessed%20with%20losing%20in%202020.%20He's%20clearly%20unhinged%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20something%20%26quot%3Bsnapped%26quot%3B%20in%20Trump%20after%20that%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFolks%2C%20Trump%20isn't%20running%20to%20lead%20America.%20He's%20running%20for%20revenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20let%20this%20man%20become%20president.%20Our%20children's%20future%20is%20at%20stake...%20We%20have%20to%20win%20this%20race%2C%20not%20for%20me%20but%20for%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20Biden%20was%20due%20to%20address%20students%20at%20Morehouse%20College%2C%20a%20renowned%20historically%20Black%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGun%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20campaigning%20in%20Texas%20during%20the%20weekend%20break%20for%20his%20criminal%20trial%20in%20New%20York.%20He%20also%20faces%20criminal%20charges%20in%20Washington%2C%20Georgia%20and%20Florida%20--%20indictments%20the%20former%20president%20routinely%20claims%20are%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20Biden%20to%20prevent%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20150-year-old%20NRA%2C%20whose%20longtime%20CEO%20resigned%20in%20January%20amid%20a%20graft%20lawsuit%2C%20is%20closely%20aligned%20with%20the%20Republican%20Party%20in%20opposing%20firearm%20restrictions%2C%20despite%20routine%20mass%20killings%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20high%20rates%20of%20gun%20violence%20compared%20to%20peer%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20at%20broad%20reforms%20to%20gun%20laws%20have%20been%20stymied%20for%20decades%2C%20with%20executive%20actions%20and%20state%20initiatives%20attacked%20in%20court%20by%20critics%20as%20infringing%20on%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20own%20a%20firearm%2C%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Second%20Amendment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20previewed%20the%20tone%20of%20his%20speech%20on%20Friday%2C%20telling%20a%20fundraising%20dinner%20in%20Minnesota%20that%20gun%20owners%20must%20vote%20Republican%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Democrats%20want%20to%20take%20their%20guns%20away%20--%20and%20they%20will%20take%20their%20guns%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20a%20long-lapsed%20ban%20on%20military%20style%20assault%20weapons%20to%20be%20reinstated%2C%20among%20other%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20White%20House%20moved%20to%20cr