minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20they%20asked%20for%20the%20phone%20password%20of%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20with%20the%20chief%20minister%20since%202015%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20given%20to%20them.%20Alleging%20that%20the%20official%20had%20destroyed%20evidence%2C%20they%20said%20the%20cellphone%20was%20formatted%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20he%20had%20claimed%20he%20had%20done%20so%20because%20it%20had%20hung.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaying%20out%20the%20reasons%20for%20seeking%20his%20custody%2C%20the%20police%20said%20he%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20an%20expert%20would%20also%20be%20needed%20to%20unlock%20the%20phone%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20without%20his%20presence.%20Custodial%20interrogation%20is%20also%20required%20to%20find%20out%20the%20reasons%20for%20assaulting%20the%20MP%2C%20they%20argued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Why%20The%20Delay%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibhav%20Kumar's%20lawyer%2C%20Rajiv%20Mohan%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20alleged%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Monday%20and%20the%20first%20information%20report%20was%20lodged%20on%20Thursday.%20No%20reason%20was%20given%20for%20the%20delay%2C%20he%20stressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20day's%20events%2C%20Mr%20Mohan%20said%20Ms%20Maliwal%20had%20gone%20not%20to%20the%20chief%20minister's%20office%20but%20to%20his%20residence%20without%20anybody%20asking%20her%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20time%20at%20which%20she%20went%20is%20also%20not%20the%20official%20time%20to%20meet%20anyone%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20(Ms%20Maliwal)%20are%20saying%20that%20you%20used%20to%20go%20there%20like%20this%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20it.%20What%20was%20her%20purpose%20for%20going%20to%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20that%20day%3F%20It%20is%20not%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mohan%20told%20the%20court.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20being%20on%20interim%20bail%20in%20the%20liquor%20scam%20case%20till%20June%202%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20%C2%A0the%20chief%20minister%20is%20busy%20since%20it%20is%20election%20time%20and%20has%20been%20given%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20days%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Ms%20Maliwal%20went%20and%20sat%20on%20a%20sofa%20in%20the%20drawing%20room%20and%20had%20the%20option%20of%20going%20back%20if%20she%20could%20not%20meet%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20video%20of%20her%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20is%20being%20circulated%20in%20the%20media%2C%20in%20which%20she%20is%20wearing%20a%20kurti%20and%20not%20a%20shirt.%20Talk%20of%20her%20buttons%20being%20open%20is%20not%20correct%20and%20neither%20is%20talk%20of%20her%20head%20banging%20against%20the%20central%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mohan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20of%20distorting%20the%20facts%2C%20Mr%20Mohan%20asked%20why%20the%20AAP%20leader%20had%20not%20filed%20an%20FIR%20when%20she%20had%20called%20a%20police%20helpline%2C%20112%2C%20from%20the%20residence%20itself.%20He%20said%20she%20must%20have%20got%20a%20response%20in%20the%20posh%20area%20but%20did%20not%20ask%20for%20any%20medical%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20that%20Ms%20Maliwal%20met%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20Police%20Station%20and%20asked%20why%20the%20officer%20had%20not%20made%20a%20medical%20sheet%20if%20there%20was%20a%20grievous%20injury.%20He%20also%20questioned%20why%20she%20didn't%20register%20a%20complaint%20at%20the%20police%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Entered%20Without%20Permission'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20entered%20there%20(the%20chief%20minister's%20residence)%20without%20permission%2C%20this%20is%20a%20crime.%20The%20section%20officer%20of%20the%20security%20staff%20had%20given%20a%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20added%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ruled%20that%20no%20one%20can%20be%20pressured%20to%20share%20their%20phone's%20password%20and%20also%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20there%20was%20no%20CCTV%20camera%20in%20the%20drawing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Tis%20Hazari%20court%20had%20rejected%20Mr%20Kumar's%20anticipatory%20bail%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20infructuous%20since%20had%20already%20been%20arrested.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%2C%20Advocate%20Shadan%20Farasat%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20was%20arrested%20when%20the%20anticipatory%20bail%20petition%20was%20being%20heard%20so%20that%20it%20became%20ineffective.%20He%20said%20the%20official%20was%20not%20told%20the%20grounds%20for%20his%20arrest%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%20Accusation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20these%20arguments%2C%20the%20lawyer%20appearing%20for%20the%20police%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20delay%20in%20filing%20an%20FIR%20and%20said%20Ms%20Maliwal%20was%20disturbed%20that%20an%20old%20acquaintance%20of%20hers%20had%20assaulted%20her.%20On%20the%20bail%20issue%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20there%20is%20no%20judgment%20that%20stops%20the%20police%20from%20effecting%20an%20arrest%20when%20an%20anticipatory%20bail%20hearing%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20video%20brought%20up%20by%20the%20defence%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20it%20was%20given%20to%20the%20media%20and%20not%20to%20the%20police%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20earlier%20been%20accused%20of%20threatening%20a%20government%20official%20in%20Noida%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716060300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpra3im7_bibhav-kumar-_625x300_16_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F