%20in%20Pahalgam%20today%20that%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20two%20tourists%20followed%20by%20another%20attack%20on%20a%20(former)%20sarpanch%20in%20Hirpora%2C%20Shopian%20-%20the%20timing%20of%20these%20attacks%20given%20that%20the%20south%20election%20was%20delayed%20without%20any%20reason%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20concern.%20Especially%20keeping%20in%20mind%20normalcy%20claims%20touted%20by%20GOI%20(Government%20of%20India).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20vice%20president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20also%20condemned%20the%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20said%20that%20such%20acts%20of%20brutality%20remain%20a%20serious%20impediment%20to%20achieving%20long-term%20peace%20in%20J-K.%20They%20urged%20all%20communities%20to%20come%20together%20in%20these%20challenging%20times%20and%20support%20efforts%20towards%20lasting%20harmony.%20Their%20thoughts%20and%20prayers%20are%20with%20the%20victims%20and%20their%20families%20during%20this%20difficult%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20killing%20of%20ex-sarpanch%20Aijaz%20Ahmad%20Sheikh%20in%20Hirpora%2C%20Shopian%2C%20South%20Kashmir%2C%20by%20terrorists%20today.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAijaz%20Ahmad%20was%20a%20brave%20soldier%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20BJP%20firmly%20stands%20with%20the%20family%20of%20Aijaz%20Ahmad%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20this%20terror%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20a%20government%20employee%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unidentified%20gunmen%20in%20a%20targeted%20attack%20as%20he%20came%20out%20of%20a%20mosque%20at%20Shadra%20Sharief%20area%20of%20Rajouri.%20He%20died%20of%20his%20injuries%20in%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2017%2C%20a%20migrant%20work