asic%20income.%20%3Cp%3EYouTube%20Screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%20is%20worried%20that%20AI%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Blots%20of%20mundane%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHinton%20advised%20the%20British%20government%20to%20establish%20universal%20basic%20income%20to%20mitigate%20AI's%20impact.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHinton%20pioneered%20neural%20networks%2C%20which%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-productivity-boost-job-performance-inequality-economics-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20will%20be%20a%20great%20equalizer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20say%20it's%20bound%20to%20widen%20the%20wealth%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-godfather-top-names-possibilities-dangers-openai-chatgpt-list-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-godfather-top-names-possibilities-dangers-openai-chatgpt-list-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20godfather%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20work%20pioneering%20neural%20networks%2C%20is%20a%20vocal%20member%20of%20the%20latter%20group.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcnd607ekl99o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20worried%20about%20AI%20taking%20lots%20of%20mundane%20jobs.%26quot%3B%20And%20he%20believes%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%20might%20be%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20consulted%20by%20people%20in%20Downing%20Street%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20advised%20them%20that%20universal%20basic%20income%20was%20a%20good%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-people-spend-universal-basic-income-ubi-food-housing-transportation-2024-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUBI%2520generally%2520refers%2520to%2520a%2Cexclusively%2520to%2520Business%2520Insider%2520subscribers.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20recurring%20cash%20payment%20made%20to%20all%20adults%20in%20a%20certain%20population%20regardless%20of%20their%20wealth%20and%20employment%20status%20%E2%80%94%20with%20no%20restrictions%20on%20how%20they%20spend%20the%20money.%20It's%20become%20a%20hot%20topic%20among%20AI%20researchers%2C%20futurists%2C%20and%20industry%20leaders%20as%20a%20way%20to%20mitigate%20AI's%20economic%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20also%20gaining%20attention%20in%20countries%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fautonomy.work%2Fportfolio%2Fsouth-africa-ubi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-study-kenya-redefining-nature-of-work-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKenya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findia-indian-government-set-to-endorse-universal-basic-income-free-money-economic-survey-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20way%20to%20tackle%20poverty.%20And%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20numerous%20cities%20and%20some%20states%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-states-cities-have-guaranteed-basic-income-programs-low-income-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperimented%20with%20guaranteed%20basic%20incomes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20give%20no-strings-attached%20monthly%20payments%20but%20to%20a%20targeted%20group%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hinton's%20view%2C%20AI%20will%20boost%20productivity%20and%20generate%20more%20wealth.%20But%20unless%20the%20government%20intervenes%2C%20it%20will%20only%20make%20the%20rich%20richer%20