%20five%20men%20were%20killed%20on%20Wednesday%20during%20a%20battle%20in%20a%20densely%20populated%20part%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20incident%20of%20friendly%20fire%20%E2%80%94%20five%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoshani%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bunder%20review%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F05%2F16%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-soldiers-killed-gaza-tank-fire.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CThere%2520was%2520an%2520incident%2520of%2Cwhen%2520two%2520tanks%2520opened%2520fire.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20tanks%20had%20fired%20at%20a%20building%20in%20the%20Jabalia%20refugee%20camp%20after%20spotting%20a%20gun%20barrel%20they%20believed%20belonged%20to%20enemy%20forces%2C%20an%20initial%20IDF%20investigation%20found%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2F5-soldiers-killed-7-hurt-in-friendly-fire-incident-in-northern-gazas-jabaliya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20were%20part%20of%20the%20IDF's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2F59780%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParatroopers%20Brigade%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e70c0bc1-a73d-4bdb-84d4-1148679c86cb%5C%22%3EFriendly%20fire%20incidents%20are%20a%20serious%20problem%20for%20the%20IDF%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFriendly%20fire%20incidents%20have%20become%20increasingly%20common%20in%20Israel's%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20outlet%20Haaretz%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%2022%20soldiers%20had%20already%20been%20killed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20friendly%20fire%20incidents%20during%20the%20conflict.%3C%2F