0there%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20%3Cem%3Elaal%20maas%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20the%20one%20cooked%20in%20Jodhpur%20where%20ghee%20is%20used%2C%20and%20the%20one%20cooked%20in%20Udaipur%20with%20mustard%20oil.%20It%20adds%20that%20the%20addition%20of%20tomatoes%20is%20highly%20debated%20as%20is%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20consistency%2C%20with%20some%20versions%20being%20saucier%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20recipe%20by%20Chef%20Ranveer%20Brar%20who%20got%20the%20recipe%20from%20Jodhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20marination%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%20kg%20mutton%2C%20curry%20cuts%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%20tbsp%20ginger%20garlic%20paste%20(70%20percent%20garlic%20%2B%2030%20percent%20ginger)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20gravy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%BC%20cup%20ghee%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2-3%20cloves%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10%20black%20peppercorns%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%20small%20cardamoms%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%20black%20cardamom%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E250%20gm%20onion%2C%20sliced%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarinated%20mutton%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalt%20to%20taste%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E20%20Mathania%20chilli%20paste%20(use%20soaked%20chillies)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E200%20gm%20curd%2C%20beaten%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%C2%BD%20tbsp%20coriander%20powder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%BD%20tsp%20red%20chilli%20powder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%BD%20tsp%20cumin%20powder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%20tbsp%20mustard%20oil%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMethod%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20marination%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%201%3A%20In%20a%20mixing%20bowl%2C%20add%20mutton%20and%20ginger%20garlic%20paste%2C%20and%20marinate%20well.%20Keep%20it%20aside%20for%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20gravy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%201%3A%20In%20a%20large%20sauce%20pot%2C%20heat%20ghee%20and%20add%20cloves%2C%20black%20peppercorns%2C%20small%20cardamoms%2C%20and%20black%20cardamom.%20Let%20the%20whole%20spices%20splutter.%3C%2F