trition.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20his%20desire%20to%20create%20impact%20first%20materialised%20as%20a%20self-book%20called%20Selfienomics%20in%202016%2C%20which%20interestingly%20had%20information%20on%20reading%20food%20labels!%20While%20he%20had%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20topic%2C%20it%20was%20seven%20years%20later%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20the%20mission%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20%E2%80%98Bournvita%E2%80%99%20video%20that%20led%20to%20him%20becoming%20a%20bonafide%20viral%20sensation%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20April%202023%2C%20Revant%20worked%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%20His%20stint%20at%20the%20management%20consulting%20firm%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20his%20content%20today.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20consultant%2C%20I%20often%20worked%20on%20projects%20in%20the%20grocery%20space%2C%20so%20I%20know%20first-hand%20about%20the%20false%20marketing%20that%20takes%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20consulting%20meant%20solving%20problems%20in%20a%20structured%20manner.%20Revant%20decided%20to%20use%20this%20skill%20to%20help%20solve%20the%20larger%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20reading%20and%20understanding%20food%20labels.%20With%20this%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20clear%20about%20his%20mission%20and%20took%20on%20the%20baton%20of%20teaching%20Indians%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20important%20life%20skill%E2%80%9D.%20His%20problem%20lies%20with%20packaged%20food%20that%20masquerades%20as%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20he%20kicked%20off%20his%20stint%20as%20%E2%80%98Foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20video%20about%20Bournvita%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Mondelez.%20The%20video%20highlighted%20the%20excessive%20amount%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20drink%2C%20yet%20calling%20itself%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20diabetes.%20The%20video%20went%20viral%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20trouble%20for%20the%20former%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20sent%20him%20a%20legal%20notice%20asking%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video.%20Left%20with%20no%20choice%2C%20Revant%20took%20it%20down%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20achieved%20what%20he%20set%20out%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20create%20awareness%20among%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStay%20away%20from%20sugary%20drinks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20legal%20notice%2C%20Cadbury%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20by%2014.4%20percent%20in%20December%202023%2C%20validating%20the%20content%20creator%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20The%20Central%20Government%20also%20directed%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20Bournvita%20and%20other%20such%20drinks%20from%20the%20health%20drinks%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20product%20that%20reduced%20its%20sugar%20content%20by%2022%20percent%20was%20%E2%80%98Maggi%20rich%20tomato%20ketchup%E2%80%99.%20Revant%20made%20a%20video%20highlighting%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20product%20had%20more%20sugar%20than%20tomatoes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%20have%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20content%20creator%2C%20who%20has%20since%20educated%20Indians%20on%20many%20other%20packaged%20products.%20His%20problem%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20with%20the%20false%20marketing%20by%20companies%2C%20which%20promise%20nutrition%2C%20strength%20and%20more%20for%20your%20child%2C%20when%20actually%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20filled%20with%20sugar.%20His%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20chocolates%20or%20Coke%20as%20much%20as%20with%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita%20and%20biscuits%20that%20are%20fed%20to%20children%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20have%20chocolate%20or%20Coke%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20but%20a%20child%20is%20having%20two%20glasses%20of%20Bournvita%20per%20day.%20Yet%2C%20we%20consider%20the%20one%20glass%20of%20Coke%20a%20problem%2C%20not%20realising%20the%20amount%20of%20sugar%20content%20in%20the%2014%20glasses%20of%20bournvita%20we%E2%80%99ve%20given%20our%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20educate%20people%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312870%2Fengineer-couple-quits-job-to-make-healthier-alternatives-to-traditional-ladoos-laddubox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esugar%20consumption%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Revant%20has%20created%20a%20sugarboard%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20amount%20of%20sugar%20in%20popular%20soft%20drinks.%20This%20has%20been%20replicated%20across%20many%20schools%2C%20ensuring%20that%20children%20stay%20away%20from%20these%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzyZCASLyx8%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzyZCASLyx8%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cd